            "sub-title": "Uncompromising Quality",
            "sub-content": "<p>We offer you excellence in every product we create. Each planter and stand we build starts with a community of remarkable craftspeople and carefully selected manufacturing partners who exhibit an attention to detail that matches our own. We insist on the time-consuming and expensive process of forming our planters in one-piece molds using centrifugal force and pressure to shape the solid clay. Our meticulous standards are your gain: Revival Ceramics are made to last a lifetime.<br/><br/></p>",
            "image_position": "left"
