            "sub-title": "Sustainable Focus",
            "sub-content": "<p>People and the environment are at the core of everything we do, so we focus on a conscientious approach to our business. While creating high-quality products is one leg of that approach, supporting people, and employing sustainable practices are the equally important other two. We build strong, caring relationships with our small, family-owned partners, who strive to empower their local communities. And because we believe the pursuit of profit should not come at the expense of sustainability, we look at every aspect of our business to ensure we produce our goods in the most sustainable manner possible. We are dedicated to doing our part to pave the road to a better, greener, and more sustainable future.<br/><br/></p>",
            "image_position": "right"
          }
        },
        "principle_block_i9UtU8": {
