            "sub-title": "Timeless Design",
            "sub-content": "<p>We love to bring you great design. From recreations of past classics to our original designs, Revival Ceramics are timeless, functional and versatile. We start with clean designs that fit any style, any decor. We then incorporate superb craftsmanship like the seamless, beautifully thin walls of our vessels or the delicate wood grains highlighted in our plant stands. The result is a product that continually delights our customers. Your design preferences may change, but your planter will never have to.<br/><br/></p>",
